  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the ttukbaegi earthenware pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the olive oil and cook the minced garlic for 1 minute.",
    "Add the minced pork and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "Add the chopped artichoke hearts, kalamata olives, turmeric, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the crumbly feta cheese and cook until melted and well combined.",
    "Squeeze the lemon juice over the top of the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Sprinkle the chopped parsley over the top of the skillet and serve hot."
